{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water, ½ tsp salt and oil in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket then weigh in mixed grains and add bay leaf. Steam <b>17 min\/100°C\/speed 4<b>.","Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and transfer grains to a serving bowl then stir to loosen. Empty mixing bowl.","Place cucumber, onions, red peppers, lemon juice, oil, coriander, 1 tsp salt and pepper in mixing bowl then chop <b>2 sec\/speed 5<b>. Pour over grains in serving bowl.","Place serving bowl with grains on mixing bowl lid and weigh in beetroot. Remove from lid and mix together well with spatula. Serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["800 g water","1 ½ tsp fine sea salt","1 tsp sunflower oil","200 g mixed grains (e.g. bulgar wheat, red rice and millet)","1 dried bay leaf","½ cucumber, deseeded, cut in pieces (approx. 150 g)","100 g spring onions, sliced (2-3 cm)","75 g red peppers, cut in pieces","20 g lemon juice","60 g extra virgin olive oil","1 small handful fresh coriander leaves (approx. 10 g)","1 pinch ground black pepper","150 g cooked beetroot, diced (1 cm)"]}],"id":"r115930","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-yqMH-kB9iHE\/XZVRj132BvI\/AAAAAAAAdQE\/N8pZK-olXMg1y1W89r7aqn3A4WdjoUM2ACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_rOhKfPkKGkwb6Ao3.png","title":"Mixed Grain Pilaf with Beetroot","publishedAt":"2016-10-10T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"2.6 g","fat":"11.6 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"13.6 g","calories":"706 kJ \/ 169 kcal"},"usefulItems":"serving bowl","hintsAndTricks":["Buy a packet of mixed grains that all have the same cooking time. We used a mix of bulgar wheat, red rice and millet. Adjust cooking time accordingly."],"basicInfo":["easy","5m","30m","6 portions"]}